::Prowl/Kluster::

Prowl's eyes widen as Iron Raptor pries his hand off her. He turn, his eyes 
following her to the projector, looking at her hips and up to the rest of 
her. He fights with his instincts, remaining in his place. He couldn't let 
her win that easily!

Prowl continues admiring Iron Raptor, jerking his eyes away as he sees a new 
femm enter, followed by Kluster. He sighs, waiting for Iron Raptor to respond 
to the new bot.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Kluster looks at Iron Raptor, entering the conference room. They hadn't been 
introduced yet, so he walks over to her.

"I am Kluster, commander of this ship," he says, extending a hand, "Its an 
honor to meet you."

He looks back at Battera. "That's Battera. She's here for peaceful purposes."
